# Project-specific
# - plans/ : local planning docs only
# - RELEASE_NOTES*.md, PLAN-*.md : drafts; GitHub Releases is source of truth
# - product-spec.md : internal spec, not for the repo
# - CleanShot*.png : screenshot tool default output
# - /test-*.png : ad-hoc Playwright screenshots dumped at repo root
plans/
RELEASE_NOTES*.md
PLAN-*.md
product-spec.md
CleanShot*.png
/test-*.png
